<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>OVERDUE: Vaccination Alert</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #f44336; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 10px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
        .alert { background-color: #f8d7da; border: 1px solid #f5c6cb; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>⚠️ OVERDUE VACCINATION ALERT</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="alert">
                <h2>URGENT: Vaccination Overdue</h2>
                <p><strong>{{petName}}</strong> has an overdue vaccination that requires immediate attention.</p>
            </div>
            
            <h3>Overdue Vaccination Details:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Pet:</strong> {{petName}}</li>
                <li><strong>Vaccine:</strong> {{vaccineName}}</li>
                <li><strong>Originally Scheduled:</strong> {{scheduledDate}}</li>
                <li><strong>Days Overdue:</strong> {{daysOverdue}}</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p><strong>Please contact your veterinarian immediately to schedule this vaccination.</strong></p>
            <p>Overdue vaccinations can put your pet's health at risk and may affect their ability to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Board at facilities</li>
                <li>Attend grooming appointments</li>
                <li>Participate in training classes</li>
                <li>Visit dog parks or public spaces</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated alert from your Pet Care System.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>